description:
Description
Hyndsight is Rob Hyndman's personal blog at
https://robjhyndman.com/hyndsight/. This series contains the daily
pageviews for one year, beginning 30 April 2014. The frequency is set to 7,
to allow the weekly pattern to be modelled.
title: Daily pageviews for the Hyndsight blog. 30 April 2014 to 29 April 2015.
